@node his "Program History"

					@{b}@{u}Program History@{uu}@{ub}
Key:
	» - means things to do
	· - means bugs fixed/things done

Module-Grapher was first concieved and started in March 1998.

Version 1.0 - ?/5/98 (ß-release)

	@{i}Things for a future version:@{ui}
