	»Add zoom in feature on fractal window
	»Fix horrible resizing bug in frcwin+grpwin
	»Make flags tooltype more efficient

	·Fixed prefs bug.

Version 1.05 - 30/7/98 (Bugfix/internal release)

	·Made iconify feature (needs fixing tho')
	·Made it a commodity
	·Ditched rubbish tooltypes that made the .exe huge and slow...
	·Fixed horrid config bug which made it crash nastily	
	·Added cool little logo in the corner!
	·Added window dimensions on the frc window
	·Made error codes for small internal errors

	@{i}Things for a version 1.1:@{ui}
	»Screen option
	»Newton-Raphson method
	»Add zoom feature on fractal window
	»Fix re-sizing bug on graph window
	»Add more formulae
	»Fix min/max value reset bug
	»Make sure the prog won't crash if opened and config file is incorrect!

	@{i}Things for a future version:@{ui}
	»Font sensitivity
	»Font option

Version 1.1 - 1/10/98 Full-ish release

	·Added GTMenus
	·Fixed iconify bug
	·Made it fully font sensitive (I said a future version - I lied)!
	
	@{b}Gap in development due to NetServer and general depression...@{ub}
	
	·Module-Grapher config/prefs files more stable and acceptable (ie. fixed config bug)
	·Gotta do command parsing! But how?
	·Ditched rubbish formulae that were real boring... :o
	
	@{i}Things for the next version@{ui}
	»Add command parsing if possible (at least add some more formulae
	»Spppeeeed up the fractal code
	»Definately add Newton-Raphson method (I`ll have to look that one up again ;^)
	»Kill stupid ALSFontRequest() bug in prefs saving
